data.value:
1. Make sure switchs are in the downward “RUN” & RS-485” position.
2. Once all messages scroll across the screen,the Laser parameters have to be adjusted; this can be done in the Service Menu by using Password:7378
BIAS : Service→Scan→Laser→Bias( Value :44.30 ) TEC : Service → Scan → Laser → TEC set point( Value :43.271 ) RA : Service → Scan → Laser → Ramp Ampl( Value :24.20 )
